{"tid":2341243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"估吓去到疫情完嘅時候全人類用咗幾多口罩","createTime":"2020-12-26T07:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T08:35:45.000Z","uid":300420,"like":11,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"418b4f32825c9d1e2d5a48610bbdf5ce47df1fd0","tid":2341243,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:38:37.000Z","msg":"保守估計全球有20億人有恆常帶罩習慣<br />\n預計會帶足兩年（由2020年頭開始計 其實點都會超過兩年 因為世界總有啲地方會過分恐懼）<br />\n假設所有人每日換一次<br />\n去到疫情完嘅時候就會用咗14600億個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲未計有啲人可能一日換超過一次+口罩廠賣唔出過期要扔嘅貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對唔住呀海龜BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拯救地球環境 由戒罩做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9dc46927d7645f0b2e6f5471f2352377f017b1","tid":2341243,"uid":327749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:39:10.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"a15076099ac93e68b341892334311124c228eac3","tid":2341243,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:39:10.000Z","msg":"環保撚收撚晒檔"},{"pid":"637e03b16dd7cf31d177fa28ecca7f556dbb9e72","tid":2341243,"uid":173945,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"估下人類呼吸排放咗幾多二氧化碳<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8c2f525df6ed567b82c36366dda40d6586a927","tid":2341243,"uid":300420,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a15076099ac93e68b341892334311124c228eac3","tid":2341243,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:39:10.000Z","msg":"環保撚收撚晒檔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:42:41.000Z","msg":"雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰啲全部都係假環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7298036c6e3e848dfe017e719e598377b1813b37","tid":2341243,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"你篇野 有 估計 預計  假設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9536143607c1a18c161a6069f9f41e7a70cc8fc","tid":2341243,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"637e03b16dd7cf31d177fa28ecca7f556dbb9e72","tid":2341243,"uid":173945,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"估下人類呼吸排放咗幾多二氧化碳<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"養活咗好多樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口罩嗰啲就真係純粹係廢料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老鑫一直提倡全民戒罩嘅其中一個原因就係保護環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df070b39065d97fde4561408061901c687f5f92","tid":2341243,"uid":131232,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:44:26.000Z","msg":"海龜BB唞唔到氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a24ec1ab2627b44b632838e64f42581acb06491","tid":2341243,"uid":300420,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7298036c6e3e848dfe017e719e598377b1813b37","tid":2341243,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"你篇野 有 估計 預計  假設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:44:29.000Z","msg":"如果搣走晒呢啲字嘅話<br />\n個數字會大好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446517e57a4e4971f5aa433e19be1e4e37daf4e2","tid":2341243,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7298036c6e3e848dfe017e719e598377b1813b37","tid":2341243,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"你篇野 有 估計 預計  假設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"香港人日日都最少600萬個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c00ccc0110daa58b2ace6e61bf7e267aac237a","tid":2341243,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"仲有噴洗手液全部化學劑來"},{"pid":"31a0ca31d29a1f2227a3714623cc8ce958d1591e","tid":2341243,"uid":235911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"應該要有系統咁回收♻️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申利：環保撚"},{"pid":"b881113a88b492b97f56a8ff6fff9ddfce9a4e71","tid":2341243,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4c00ccc0110daa58b2ace6e61bf7e267aac237a","tid":2341243,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"仲有噴洗手液全部化學劑來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:47:50.000Z","msg":"珍<br />\n老鑫從來唔用搓手液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家研究緊自己織個布口罩出嚟戴 就唔使戴即棄口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4af0af58adacd11c79cfcaea3b65156d0f0c0c","tid":2341243,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">環保撚仆街死啦</span>"},{"pid":"bebbb19f06923fe7de8f3246df32a65f9d9be2b8","tid":2341243,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:47:56.000Z","msg":"仲有洗手,拖地,清潔抹嘢用多咗好多水"},{"pid":"2019958c5e900ecedb2bc7067ebc2bf7813d7443","tid":2341243,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ceab4a0c0ee297be4c0aa41561111e6017a48379","tid":2341243,"uid":300420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31a0ca31d29a1f2227a3714623cc8ce958d1591e","tid":2341243,"uid":235911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"應該要有系統咁回收♻️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申利：環保撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:50:13.000Z","msg":"口罩好難回收<br />\n佢裏面嗰條鐵線唔可以同啲布料一齊處理<br />\n同埋口罩一般有幾層 每層都要有唔同嘅處理方法<br />\n仲有嗰兩條繩都唔知點搞好<br />\n<br />\n加埋其實佢算係醫療廢物嚟 有冇人肯冒險回收都係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d20c54dc0af54ea3b3ee126e8b4d4b5247accf4","tid":2341243,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2019958c5e900ecedb2bc7067ebc2bf7813d7443","tid":2341243,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"而家我大概三四日換一次<br />\n應該有其他人同我一樣<br />\n但係亦都有人係一日換超過一次嘅 其實幾難計<br />\n所以假設一人一日一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b80e7a50f41665349780f5a2ea03e117a307bf8","tid":2341243,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:00:04.000Z","msg":"老鑫相信群體免疫<br />\n因為咁樣仲可以搏吓（而且贏面仲好撚大）<br />\n但係用口罩就算捱過咗 地球嘅生態系統一樣玩完<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a65b771813e95292f54df7507a67c44d18df1a","tid":2341243,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:01:14.000Z","msg":"唔係政府強制,我都未必戴"},{"pid":"5fa5c7871c71e1c393398ac31ffc61b7b0d1f186","tid":2341243,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"78a65b771813e95292f54df7507a67c44d18df1a","tid":2341243,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:01:14.000Z","msg":"唔係政府強制,我都未必戴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:03:03.000Z","msg":"唔係政府強制 我一定唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肯定幾十年之後啲人會屌我哋當年污染環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6208730f2c3bc5f5ab296c2c7c01090016b1f5","tid":2341243,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:35:45.000Z","msg":"其實醫院日日都用好多膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解你唔抽埋"}]}